FT  06 SEP 94 / Scots screening
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Film-makers are spending an estimated Pounds 20m in Scotland this year,
almost as much as they spent in total during the past three years, film
promotion body Scottish Screen Locations said yesterday.
</TEXT>
<XX>
Countries:-
</XX>
<CN>GBZ  United Kingdom, EC.
</CN>
<XX>
Industries:-
</XX>
<IN>P7812 Motion Picture and Video Production.
</IN>
<XX>
